<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
        .emoji {
            font-size: 5rem;
            animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin {
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background-color: #4ecdc4;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            background-color: #45b7aa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="emoji">ðŸ™ƒ</div>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>Oops! The page you're looking for is playing hide and seek.</p>
        <p>We've sent our best detective to find it, but in the meantime...</p>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">Take me back home!</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
